<p><strong>Key Takeaways:</strong></p>



<ul>
<li>Mobile wallets are specially designed smartphone apps&nbsp;that&nbsp;allow users to manage their cryptocurrencies conveniently and securely</li>



<li>Popular mobile wallet options for managing crypto on smartphones include PTPWallet, Binance Wallet, Coinbase Wallet, Trust Wallet, and Luno Wallet</li>



